      17.9136 30.8133Z"/>
    </svg>
  </button>
  <div class="testimonials-slider">
    <blockquote class="testimonial-item">
      <Image src={imgTestimonial} densities={[1.5, 2]} alt="business man" class="testimonial-img" />
      <span>Jack Mayer</span>
      <p>"The courses were of exceptional quality and cutting-edge. You won't find these courses just anywhere."</p>
